title: Extend Treasury Commitee Funds
body:
Extend The Treasury Committee budget with a grant of $50000 USDC tokens from Treasury to be used within the next 3 months. 

This is an extension of this past proposal https://snapshot.org/#/nft20.eth/proposal/QmPpkPcQVHrdqMJFoxqgM9JbtscqWW96tCvcMBkdrsrVn5
author: 0x4B5922ABf25858d012d12bb1184e5d3d0B6D6BE4
